## Additional Notes on Generated Content

The MIT License above covers the scholar-wendao framework itself (SKILL.md,
references, scripts, and documentation).

**Perspective skills generated by scholar-wendao** are derivative works that
quote, paraphrase, and analyze published works of scholars. Users of this
framework are responsible for:

1. Respecting copyright when distributing generated perspective skills,
   particularly the inclusion of substantial quotations from copyrighted works
2. Following fair-use principles for academic and research purposes
3. Acknowledging the scholars whose works are being distilled
4. Understanding that perspective skills are not authorized representations
   of the scholars themselves

The five "humble epistemics" boundaries declared in references/humble-epistemics.md
must be preserved in all generated perspective skills as a condition of using
this framework.
